Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我是奧利弗•奎恩\N{\b0\fs12}My name is Oliver Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.53,0:00:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,五年裡  我被困在地獄一般的小島上\N{\b0\fs12}After five years on a hellish island,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來只有一個目標\N{\b0\fs12}I have come home with only one goal--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.45,0:00:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救我的城市\N{\b0\fs12}to save my city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但要達到目標  我不能像過去一樣成為兇手\N{\b0\fs12}But to do so, I can't be the killer I once was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,為了紀念我的朋友  我只能偽裝成另一個人\N{\b0\fs12}To honor my friend's memory, I must be someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.03,0:00:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,成為另一個存在\N{\b0\fs12}I must be something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.20,0:00:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,《綠箭俠》前情回顧\N{\b0\fs12}Previously on "Arrow"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一直追蹤的一個人\N{\b0\fs12}There's a new player we've been tracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一直叫他喪鐘\N{\b0\fs12}We've been calling him...Deathstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我有個提議給你們\N{\b0\fs12}I have a proposal for you men.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.91,0:00:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊被注射了血清\N{\b0\fs12}Roy was injected with the serum.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,還活著  不過我們得看著他\N{\b0\fs12}He's alive. But we are going to have to keep an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,遠離西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Stay away from Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.82,0:00:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不  她在你身邊的時候非常不安全\N{\b0\fs12}No. She's not safe when she's around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你愛她  所以你要按我說的做\N{\b0\fs12}You love her, and that's why you're going to do what I'm asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎能不告訴我  馬爾科姆•梅林是我父親\N{\b0\fs12}How could you not tell me Malcolm Merlyn was my father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.37,0:00:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我那麼信任你\N{\b0\fs12}I believed in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.69,0:00:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就在半小時前\N{\b0\fs12}As of 30 minutes ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.39,0:00:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你的公司歸我了\N{\b0\fs12}your company belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德  你為他工作\N{\b0\fs12}Slade. You're working for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道奧利弗•奎恩就是綠箭俠\N{\b0\fs12}I know Oliver Queen is the Arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得這個頭套眼睛開孔位置不太對\N{\b0\fs12}I don't think my eye holes line up properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人有這個問題嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is anyone else having this problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.31,0:01:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-別緊張  -我就是很緊張\N{\b0\fs12}- Don't be nervous. - I'm a lot nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,即使對我們而言  這也算是大動作\N{\b0\fs12}This is a big move, even for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我們曾經利用大動作取得制勝先機\N{\b0\fs12}And we've cornered the market on big moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德讓我們別無選擇\N{\b0\fs12}Slade didn't give us any choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,按照計劃而言  這可不是個好主意\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, as far as plans go, this is not a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,費利西蒂  這是你的計劃\N{\b0\fs12}Felicity. This was your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.92,0:01:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得你其實沒批準\N{\b0\fs12}I didn't think you'd actually say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我們到了\N{\b0\fs12}We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}羅伯特•奎恩\N應用科學中心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人曾經為我工作過\N{\b0\fs12}Hey! That man used to work for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,現在他為我們的敵人工作\N{\b0\fs12}And now he works for our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,安保攝像頭已經搞定\N{\b0\fs12}Security cameras are down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你們還記得萬能鑰匙嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You all remember the skeleton key?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:01:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉•塔克曼的禮物  就是那個同步信號之王\N{\b0\fs12}Courtesy of William Tockman, AKA the Clock King.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可以打開任何鎖  包括這一個\N{\b0\fs12}It can open any lock. Including this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我們遇見巴里的地方\N{\b0\fs12}This is where we met Barry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這些是隨插即用的\N{\b0\fs12}These are plug n' play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,把它們固定在我們說好的地方\N{\b0\fs12}Fasten them to what we talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的就交給C4炸彈吧\N{\b0\fs12}Let the C4 do the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好久沒有搞過爆炸了\N{\b0\fs12}Been a while since I've blown anything up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,速戰速決\N{\b0\fs12}Quick and clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我是個炸彈客  真不敢相信我成了炸彈客\N{\b0\fs12}I'm a bomber. I can't believe I'm a bomber.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道能不能當做特殊技能寫進簡歷裡\N{\b0\fs12}I wonder if I can list that on my resume under special skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不許動\N{\b0\fs12}Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得走了\N{\b0\fs12}We have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:02:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,熱成像顯示建築裡已經沒人了\N{\b0\fs12}Thermal shows everybody's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只是一棟建築  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}It's just a building, Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}奎恩集團回應爆炸事件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,懦夫\N{\b0\fs12}Cowards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼人會毫無必要的破壞\N{\b0\fs12}Who else would needlessly destroy cutting edge,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,尖端科學與醫療技術\N{\b0\fs12}scientific and medical technology
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.57,0:03:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而且這些技術\N{\b0\fs12}whose sole purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是為了把星城變成一個更健康更安全的地方\N{\b0\fs12}is to make Starling City a healthier and safer place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,作為奎恩集團的總裁\N{\b0\fs12}As CEO of Queen Consolidated,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我要對做下這種惡行的恐怖分子說幾句\N{\b0\fs12}I have a message to the terrorist who committed this unspeakable act.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你們將被抓住  並接受懲罰\N{\b0\fs12}You will be caught, and punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我鄭重聲明  在發現\N{\b0\fs12}For the record, I hated her
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她是個大壞蛋之前我就很討厭她\N{\b0\fs12}before we found out she was a super villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  斯萊德的目的是\N{\b0\fs12}Ok. Slade's goal is to create an army
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,利用米拉庫魯建立一支人體武器部隊\N{\b0\fs12}of human weapons using the Mirakuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,為達到這個目的  他需要工業離心機\N{\b0\fs12}To do that, he needs an industrial centrifuge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,讓伊莎貝爾•羅切夫從你的家族手中\N{\b0\fs12}Which having Isabel Rochev steal Queen Consolidated
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,奪走奎恩集團讓他可以大展拳腳\N{\b0\fs12}from your family gave him full access to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但是既然應用科學中心被炸了\N{\b0\fs12}But since Applied Sciences went kaboom,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他就沒法利用我們的技術\N{\b0\fs12}he can't use our technology--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我們以前的技術  來做他的邪惡試驗了\N{\b0\fs12}well, formerly ours for his warped science experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,幾周以來斯萊德一直緊緊相逼\N{\b0\fs12}Slade has had us on our heels for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我們跟他正面對決只是時間問題\N{\b0\fs12}It's about time we took the fight to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我們所做的一切就是為了讓他直接面對我們\N{\b0\fs12}All this will do is set him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我們無法知道下一次攻擊會來自哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}We have no way of knowing where the next attack is coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}奧利弗•奎恩回到星城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}治安維持者在星城港口槍戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}兜帽治安維持者再度來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}西婭•奎恩被兜帽男所救
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著  你必須放下這事  好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Look, you need to drop this, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事  真的\N{\b0\fs12}I'm fine. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼可能沒事\N{\b0\fs12}How is any of this fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你要把注意力放在自己身上\N{\b0\fs12}Look, you need to concentrate on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你準備去參加會議嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Now listen, are you going to your meetings?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我要去那裡說說我父親是怎麼入獄的\N{\b0\fs12}Yes. It's where I talk about how my father's facing prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這些都會過去的  好嗎  拜託了\N{\b0\fs12}This will all blow over, OK? Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不會的  爸爸\N{\b0\fs12}No. It won't, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你被抓住是因為幫助支持那個治安維持者\N{\b0\fs12}You were caught aiding and abetting the Vigilante.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,去年跟他一起合作害你丟了警長之職\N{\b0\fs12}Working with him last year cost you your detective shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,現在可能會害你入獄18個月\N{\b0\fs12}Now, it can cost you 18 months in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他們想知道他的名字\N{\b0\fs12}They want his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道綠箭俠是誰嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you know who the Arrow is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\b0\fs12}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我發誓\N{\b0\fs12}I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那黑衣女子呢\N{\b0\fs12}Ok, well, what about the woman in black?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,跟綠箭俠在一起的那個\N{\b0\fs12}The one the Arrow works with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道她是誰嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you know who she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-不知道  -那你肯定知道些什麼吧\N{\b0\fs12}- No. - Well, you must have some idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,寶貝  我沒法告訴你我不知道的事\N{\b0\fs12}Honey, I can't tell you what I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,時間到\N{\b0\fs12}Time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子們  照顧好彼此\N{\b0\fs12}You girls, you take care of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你真心覺得他不知道綠箭俠是誰嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you really think he doesn't know who the Arrow is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸不會撒謊\N{\b0\fs12}It's not like dad to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有時最親近的人  才是最具欺騙性的\N{\b0\fs12}Sometimes it's people closest to us who lie to us best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭去哪了\N{\b0\fs12}Where is Thea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她應該也要到場的\N{\b0\fs12}She should be here for this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得她不會來了\N{\b0\fs12}I doubt she's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我對你們就實話實說了\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I can't lie to either of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,情況很糟糕\N{\b0\fs12}it's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦伊莎貝爾•羅切夫掌權  就玩完了\N{\b0\fs12}If Isabel Rochev is one thing, it's thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,為了這次收購  她已經籌劃了好幾個月\N{\b0\fs12}She's been laying the foundation for this takeover for months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我們仍然持有公司大部分股票  對吧\N{\b0\fs12}But we still own a majority of stock in the company, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  但是伊莎貝爾削弱了股票的價值\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, but Isabel has diluted that stock
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,現在來說  它們分文不值\N{\b0\fs12}to the point where it's worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在名義上  你們真的破產了\N{\b0\fs12}On paper, you're virtually broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼好消息是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}And what's the good news?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可以保護你們的資產\N{\b0\fs12}We can protect your assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我們需要把所有的財產\N{\b0\fs12}We need to move everything
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,轉移到伊莎貝爾碰不到的地方\N{\b0\fs12}into a new trust that Isabel can't touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要當下所有受惠人的簽名\N{\b0\fs12}All I need is the beneficiaries from the current trust
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,來授權此次財產轉移\N{\b0\fs12}to approve the transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是你們兩位  還有西婭\N{\b0\fs12}The two of you and Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭也需要簽字\N{\b0\fs12}Thea needs to sign off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  而且是馬上\N{\b0\fs12}Yes. And quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你  奈德\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you, Ned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,現在  我不得不成為市長了\N{\b0\fs12}Well, now I have to become mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我需要這份工資\N{\b0\fs12}It seems I'll need the income.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,失去公司  不是你的錯\N{\b0\fs12}Losing the company wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的錯\N{\b0\fs12}It was mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我敗給了伊莎貝爾•羅切夫\N{\b0\fs12}I let Isabel Rochev get the better of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不是  你總是能看到別人好的一面\N{\b0\fs12}No. You always see the good in people,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕他們不值得你如此\N{\b0\fs12}even if they don't deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我比誰都清楚這一點\N{\b0\fs12}I know that better than most.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莎貝爾報仇心切\N{\b0\fs12}Isabel is a vindictive woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你信任她與否  她都要達到目的\N{\b0\fs12}She would have done this with or without your trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道\N{\b0\fs12}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你幾個月前告訴過我  不能相信她\N{\b0\fs12}You told me months ago I couldn't trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你父親  容易屈服於\N{\b0\fs12}Your father had a weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,美麗  並且強勢的女人\N{\b0\fs12}for beautiful, strong women.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在一起過\N{\b0\fs12}They were together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\b0\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,當年她還是商學院的學生\N{\b0\fs12}She was still in business school at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,美麗的實習生頗受總裁的青睞\N{\b0\fs12}The pretty intern that caught the CEO's eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你把這個拿給西婭\N{\b0\fs12}You take this to Thea,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,無論如何說服她  幫助我們反擊\N{\b0\fs12}and you convince her somehow, to help us fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-能幫我一把嗎  -好的\N{\b0\fs12}- Will you help me up? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-去我的箱子那  -好的 \N{\b0\fs12}- Just to my trunk. - Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧看誰起來啦\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, look who's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,正好趕上看好戲\N{\b0\fs12}Just in time for all the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你要對他做什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What are you going to do to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,聽聽他的尖叫聲\N{\b0\fs12}Make him scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就像他對我們所做的\N{\b0\fs12}Just like he made us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,俗話說  活下來就是最好的復仇\N{\b0\fs12}They say living well is best revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得折磨才是\N{\b0\fs12}I prefer torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你想第一個來嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You want first turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不要  拜託\N{\b0\fs12}No, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我能幫助你們\N{\b0\fs12}I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不  博士  我能幫助你\N{\b0\fs12}No, doctor. I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你說過的  研究需要什麼來著\N{\b0\fs12}What was it you said you needed for research?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,一隻眼睛\N{\b0\fs12}An eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\b0\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我給你弄一隻新鮮的\N{\b0\fs12}Let me get you a fresh one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你們還是可以阻止斯萊德•威爾遜的\N{\b0\fs12}You can still stop Slade Wilson!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,阿納托利  慢著\N{\b0\fs12}Anatoly. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛剛說什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我能幫助你們阻止他\N{\b0\fs12}I can help you stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼阻止  你的神藥已經把他變成了怪物\N{\b0\fs12}How? That miracle drug has turned him into monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  我能讓他變回來\N{\b0\fs12}I know. I can turn him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,艾沃  你在說什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Ivo, what are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,米拉庫魯  它有解藥\N{\b0\fs12}The Mirakuru. There's a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭在這裡嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, is Thea here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有見到她\N{\b0\fs12}No, I haven't seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸還好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}How's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,為了綠箭俠進監獄  他心甘情願\N{\b0\fs12}He's willing to go to jail for the Arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你說不擔心 \N{\b0\fs12}I know you said you weren't worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但是狄格和我還是去了羅伊的公寓\N{\b0\fs12}but Dig and I went to Roy's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,現在人去樓空\N{\b0\fs12}It's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去像是幾天前就搬走了\N{\b0\fs12}Seems like he cleared out a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他會去哪呢\N{\b0\fs12}Where the hell did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊的事暫時緩一緩\N{\b0\fs12}Roy will have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們現在要考慮的是斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}We need to deal with Slade,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,弄清楚他下一步的行動\N{\b0\fs12}figure out what his next move is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我瞭解斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}I know Slade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他不會停手的  除非...\N{\b0\fs12}He is not going to stop till...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回家\N{\b0\fs12}Welcome home
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}Hello, Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,狄格爾  退後\N{\b0\fs12}Diggle, stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在浪費子彈\N{\b0\fs12}You're wasting your bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,小子  別忘了是誰教你打架的\N{\b0\fs12}Don't forget who taught you how to fight, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  我在找我妹妹莎拉•蘭斯\N{\b0\fs12}Excuse me, I'm looking for my sister, Sara Lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\b0\fs12}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我是勞蕾爾•蘭斯  我妹妹還好嗎\N{\b0\fs12}I'm Laurel Lance. Is my sister ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,她沒事的  手腕部有細微骨裂\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, she'll be fine. Just a hairline fracture of her wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,已經處理過了\N{\b0\fs12}We set it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,淤青挺嚇人的  看上去以為傷得很重\N{\b0\fs12}She's got some nasty bruises, looks worse than it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,與她的舊患相比  這不算什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Nothing compared to her previous injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼舊患\N{\b0\fs12}Previous...injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  你妹妹全身上下\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, your sister has extensive scar tissue
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,都有大量的瘢痕組織\N{\b0\fs12}over her entire body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我上一次見到帶有如此多傷痕的人\N{\b0\fs12}The last person I saw with that much damage
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是一名在伊拉克受傷的退伍軍人\N{\b0\fs12}was a veteran injured in Iraq.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你妹妹服過役嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Has your sister served in the military?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有\N{\b0\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,她沒服過役\N{\b0\fs12}No, she hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-你來了  -到底發生了什麼事\N{\b0\fs12}- Hey. - What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利和我騎摩托車時摔了一下而已\N{\b0\fs12}Ollie and I just had a little motorcycle mishap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的\N{\b0\fs12}It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經辦好出院手續了\N{\b0\fs12}I already got my discharge papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你的背...\N{\b0\fs12}But your back...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那些傷痕  是怎麼來的\N{\b0\fs12}Those scars, where did you get them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧\N{\b0\fs12}You OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,會沒事的  你呢\N{\b0\fs12}I will be. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我也沒事  勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah. Yeah. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你來了  告訴我到底怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}Hi. So tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,摩托車禍  笨死了\N{\b0\fs12}Motorcycle accident. It was stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我們正要左拐時  一輛車闖了紅燈\N{\b0\fs12}We were making a left turn, this car ran a red light.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你們錄口供了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Did you file a police report?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒那個必要  我們倆都沒事\N{\b0\fs12}We didn't see the point. We're both fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這才是最重要的  不是嗎\N{\b0\fs12}That's-- that's what counts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\b0\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的該走了\N{\b0\fs12}I should really go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.99,0:13:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一小時後我還要上庭\N{\b0\fs12}I have a deposition in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\b0\fs12}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你來看我\N{\b0\fs12}Thanks for checking up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,當然\N{\b0\fs12}Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道奧利弗•奎恩就是綠箭俠\N{\b0\fs12}I know Oliver Queen is the Arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}威登酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\b0\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你昨天沒去開會\N{\b0\fs12}We missed you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,跟奈德•福斯特的會\N{\b0\fs12}The meeting with Ned Foster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭  我知道你在生我和媽的氣\N{\b0\fs12}Thea, I know that you're mad at mom and me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們也許有辦法解決這次金融危機\N{\b0\fs12}but we may have found a way out of this financial mess
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不會失去一切的\N{\b0\fs12}where we aren't going to lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽和我都簽字了  我們...\N{\b0\fs12}Mom and I both signed, we just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我們需要你的簽名\N{\b0\fs12}We need your signature,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,希望能阻止伊莎貝爾毀了我們\N{\b0\fs12}and hopefully we can stop Isabel from ruining us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你是說在你讓她毀了我們之後\N{\b0\fs12}After you let her ruin us, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡說到西婭•奎恩\N{\b0\fs12}It says Thea Queen here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那是誰\N{\b0\fs12}Who's she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你  閃電妞\N{\b0\fs12}That's you, Speedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我\N{\b0\fs12}No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伯特•奎恩不是我父親\N{\b0\fs12}Robert Queen wasn't my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,馬爾科姆•梅林才是\N{\b0\fs12}Malcolm Merlyn was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭•梅林\N{\b0\fs12}Thea Merlyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這個名字挺好聽的\N{\b0\fs12}Kind of has a nice ring to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,梅林只是你的生父  是老爸養大你的\N{\b0\fs12}Merlyn was your biological father, but Dad raised you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因為他不知道我不是他親生的\N{\b0\fs12}Only because he didn't know I wasn't his.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他很愛你的\N{\b0\fs12}He...He loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是  我仍然還是你哥哥\N{\b0\fs12}So do I, and I am still your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是  你是我同母異父的哥哥\N{\b0\fs12}No, you're not. You're my half brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我另一個同母異父的哥哥是誰嗎\N{\b0\fs12}And you know who else was my half brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是湯米\N{\b0\fs12}Tommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾經想要吻的那個湯米\N{\b0\fs12}Tommy, who I tried to kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾經想要吻我同母異父的哥哥\N{\b0\fs12}I tried to kiss my half brother--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,之後我親生父親竟然把他殺了\N{\b0\fs12}before my real father killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人生就是這麼複雜\N{\b0\fs12}That's how screwed up I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嗎  最難過的是\N{\b0\fs12}And you know the sad part,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,之前我的生活竟然要開始漸入佳境了\N{\b0\fs12}I was actually starting to be in a good place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我有間夜店  有羅伊\N{\b0\fs12}I had the club, I had Roy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有個對我說實話的哥哥\N{\b0\fs12}I had a brother who wasn't lying to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,在我混亂的生活中第一次\N{\b0\fs12}And for the first time in my crazy life,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的一切還算過得去\N{\b0\fs12}everything didn't seem so completely and totally messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為我的人生會變好\N{\b0\fs12}I thought I was going to be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我實在太蠢了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你一點也不蠢\N{\b0\fs12}You're not stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我是...\N{\b0\fs12}No, what I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,兩個殺人成性的人的女兒\N{\b0\fs12}is the daughter of two mass murderers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不止一個  是兩個\N{\b0\fs12}Not one, but two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,面對現實吧  奧利\N{\b0\fs12}So let's face it, Ollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人生是不會變好的\N{\b0\fs12}I was never going to be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我的基因註定如此\N{\b0\fs12}It's not in my genes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Thea...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我們現在要討論安全措施的問題\N{\b0\fs12}We need to discuss that security matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,情況如何\N{\b0\fs12}What do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-斯萊德拿走的東西  -拿走的東西\N{\b0\fs12}- What Slade took. - Took?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是來殺我們的\N{\b0\fs12}He wasn't here to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他來是因為我們手上有他想要的東西\N{\b0\fs12}He was here because we had something that he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那把萬能鑰匙\N{\b0\fs12}The Skeleto Key.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了全面檢查  只有這把鑰匙不見了\N{\b0\fs12}I did a full sweep. It's the only thing that's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,現在他需要一種新方式來大規模生產血清\N{\b0\fs12}He needs a new way to mass produce the serum now that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我們炸毀了應用科學中心\N{\b0\fs12}we've dusted Applied Sciences.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,擁有萬能鑰匙\N{\b0\fs12}With the Skeleton Key,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他能進入任何地方  拿到任何想要的東西\N{\b0\fs12}he can get into anywhere and take anything he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我們知道他想要什麼\N{\b0\fs12}We know what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,只需要先他一步找到\N{\b0\fs12}We just need to find it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,星城最先進的技術\N{\b0\fs12}Where is the most cutting edge technology housed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.19,0:16:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}in Starling City?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}星級實驗室  星城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}星級實驗室  倉庫數據庫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這是每個曾在星級實驗室\N{\b0\fs12}The combined inventory of every scientist
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,工作過的科學家的數據\N{\b0\fs12}who ever worked at S.T.A.R. Labs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的都在這裡\N{\b0\fs12}All housed right in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我將這棟大樓命名為"屌炸天"\N{\b0\fs12}I hereby christen this building "Da bomb."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,現在沒人這麼說了\N{\b0\fs12}Nobody says that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我就這麼說\N{\b0\fs12}I say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哥就是這麼酷\N{\b0\fs12}I define my own cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是難以相信威爾斯博士竟要關掉這個地方\N{\b0\fs12}I still can't believe Dr. Wells is shutting this place down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,尖端科研實驗室在我們打開粒子加速器時\N{\b0\fs12}S.T.A.R. Labs blew a hole in Central City
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在中心城市內引起了大爆炸\N{\b0\fs12}when we turned the particle accelerator on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,星城要終止\N{\b0\fs12}It's not surprising that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,對這個設施的租賃也在情理之中\N{\b0\fs12}Starling City cancelled the lease on this facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"讓我們來保管社區內無人管理的樣機吧"\N{\b0\fs12}We're not exactly the poster children for
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我們這麼說了  但卻沒有做到\N{\b0\fs12}"Let us store our unregulated prototypes in your neighborhood."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那是個意外  凱特琳\N{\b0\fs12}It was an accident, Caitlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,跟受害者家屬\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, well, try telling
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,也這麼說試試看吧\N{\b0\fs12}that to the families of the people who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,或許你應該先想想怎麼給自己一個交代\N{\b0\fs12}Maybe you can figure out how to tell that to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:17:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,西斯科  把庫存盤點完  我們就能回家了\N{\b0\fs12}Look, Cisco, let's get this inventory done so we can go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為這裡沒別人了\N{\b0\fs12}I thought we were the only ones here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,或許是其中一個警衛\N{\b0\fs12}Maybe it's one of the security guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊\N{\b0\fs12}Oh. Hey, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我們馬上就能結束了\N{\b0\fs12}We should be wrapped up any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你有沒有一種不祥的預感\N{\b0\fs12}Are you getting a bad vibe off this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你讓我追你的時間越長\N{\b0\fs12}The longer you make me chase you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我折磨你的時間就越長\N{\b0\fs12}the slower I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,幫幫我\N{\b0\fs12}Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這個設備本屬於亞瑟•萊特\N{\b0\fs12}This equipment belonged to Arthur Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,威爾斯兩年前把他炒了\N{\b0\fs12}Wells fired him two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-為什麼  -因為他是個瘋子\N{\b0\fs12}- Why? - Because he was a psycho.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你可千萬要搞定這東西啊\N{\b0\fs12}Please tell me you can make this work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}禁區  只有特準人員可進
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我收回我剛說的話\N{\b0\fs12}I take back what I said--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我會速戰速決的\N{\b0\fs12}I'll make this quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs12}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:18:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我們來晚了\N{\b0\fs12}We're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-費利西蒂  -西斯科  凱特琳\N{\b0\fs12}- Felicity! - Cisco, Caitlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你們還好嗎  他沒傷害你們吧  他沒有吧\N{\b0\fs12}Are you guys ok? He didn't hurt you, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你說了兩次"他"\N{\b0\fs12}You said "he" twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道襲擊我們的人是誰嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you know who attacked us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那個戴著面具手拿長劍的瘋子\N{\b0\fs12}That lunatic with the mask and the sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不知道\N{\b0\fs12}Uh, no. I--no, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我說了兩遍"他"  因為我聽到廣播裡說\N{\b0\fs12}I--I said "he" twice, because on the radio,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,襲擊你們的那個人有男性特徵\N{\b0\fs12}I heard that the person who attacked you had man parts,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我認為他是個男的\N{\b0\fs12}which would make him a...he.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫約翰•狄格爾  奎恩聯合企業的保安\N{\b0\fs12}I'm John Diggle, I work security for Queen Consolidated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道面具男拿走什麼了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Do you have any idea what the masked man may have taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,比如一臺工業離心機之類的\N{\b0\fs12}an industrial centrifuge, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,無可奉告  這是個秘密\N{\b0\fs12}No. It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼樣的秘密\N{\b0\fs12}What kind of secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不能說的秘密\N{\b0\fs12}The kind I have to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,西斯科也得保守這個秘密嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Well, does Cisco have to keep it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-沒錯  -好吧\N{\b0\fs12}- Yes. He does. - Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我們很高興看到你們倆都沒事\N{\b0\fs12}We're just so happy that you guys are ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,巴里怎麼樣了\N{\b0\fs12}How's Barry doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,老樣子\N{\b0\fs12}He's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,巴里的情況惡化了\N{\b0\fs12}Barry's condition deteriorated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他們把他移到了尖端科技研究實驗室內照顧他\N{\b0\fs12}They moved him to S.T.A.R. Labs. They've been looking after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是因此而認識西斯科和凱特琳的 \N{\b0\fs12}That's how I met Cisco and Caitlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\b0\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我一有空就會再去看他的\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I'll come visit again, as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那很好\N{\b0\fs12}That would be cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心  很多人都來看巴里\N{\b0\fs12}Don't worry, Barry gets lots of visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,艾麗絲經常去那兒\N{\b0\fs12}Iris is there a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,艾麗絲嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Iris?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,她是\N{\b0\fs12}She's, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他的\N{\b0\fs12}his...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,某人\N{\b0\fs12}Something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此\N{\b0\fs12}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧\N{\b0\fs12}Sure. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真了不起\N{\b0\fs12}That's just swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,巴里還在昏迷中就已經有進展了\N{\b0\fs12}Barry's in a coma and he's already moved on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我侵入了哈里森•威爾斯的個人檔案\N{\b0\fs12}I hacked into Harrison Wells' personal files.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他是尖端科技研究實驗室的主管\N{\b0\fs12}He's the director S.T.A.R. Labs,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以這差不多讓我可以查看任何資料\N{\b0\fs12}which basically makes me unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我發現了什麼\N{\b0\fs12}And look what I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這是他們其中一個生物技術項目的原型\N{\b0\fs12}It's a prototype for one of their new bio-tech projects.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.09,0:20:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒有申請到專利\N{\b0\fs12}The patent is still pending,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,或許這就是為什麼他們不想告訴我們\N{\b0\fs12}which is probably why they didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那到底是什麼東西\N{\b0\fs12}want to tell us what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,所以這到底是什麼\N{\b0\fs12}So what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這是個生物傳輸導管\N{\b0\fs12}It's a biotransfuser.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,它可以同時把血液從一個病人體內\N{\b0\fs12}It can deliver blood from one single patient
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,輸入到多個病人體內\N{\b0\fs12}into multiple patients, at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼斯萊德需要輸血\N{\b0\fs12}Why would Slade need a blood transfusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他不需要\N{\b0\fs12}He doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但他為了創建自己的私人軍隊\N{\b0\fs12}The prisoners that he freed from Iron Heights last week
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,上周從鐵山監獄放走的那些囚犯需要\N{\b0\fs12}to create his own personal army do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,稍作調整  斯萊德就可以將它改造\N{\b0\fs12}With a few tweaks, Slade can retro-fit it for the Mirakuru,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,用於米拉庫魯  而且他完全不用顧忌\N{\b0\fs12}bypassing what we know to be a less than desirable
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,失敗之後死亡率很高的問題\N{\b0\fs12}ratio of success to, you know, death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.87,0:21:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這一切都將會在機器內進行\N{\b0\fs12}Instead of it metabolizing in the person,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是利用人體內新陳代謝\N{\b0\fs12}it happens in the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.50,0:21:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這得需要大量的血液才行啊\N{\b0\fs12}That's going to require a whole lot of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,即使耐力非凡的斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}Even a man with Slade's stamina
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,也承受不住那種血液流乾的痛苦\N{\b0\fs12}can't handle that kind of drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-很好  -你什麼意思\N{\b0\fs12}- Good. - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就讓他使用\N{\b0\fs12}We let him use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他會變得虛弱  不堪一擊\N{\b0\fs12}He'll be weak, vulnerable,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那時候就是我殺死他的好時機\N{\b0\fs12}and that will be my opportunity to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我們怎麼才能找到這個東西\N{\b0\fs12}How do we find this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要啟動這樣的機器\N{\b0\fs12}A machine like this pulls an exorbitant
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,需要大量的電力支援\N{\b0\fs12}amount of power from the grid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,當它啟動時  我就會知道時間和地點\N{\b0\fs12}When it turns on, I'll know when and where.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,現在  我們只能靜心等待\N{\b0\fs12}Right now, we just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我受夠無盡等待了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm tired of waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,別聽他的  他在撒謊\N{\b0\fs12}Don't listen to him, he's lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,解藥真的存在  我保證\N{\b0\fs12}The cure is real, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不  他只是想要活命才會這麼說的\N{\b0\fs12}No, he's just trying to save his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.03,0:22:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,安東尼  看著我\N{\b0\fs12}Anthony, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我們解藥的事\N{\b0\fs12}Tell us about the cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我想幫助你  莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}I want to help you, Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但首先  你要保證你也會幫我\N{\b0\fs12}But first, you have to promise you'll help me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她救不了你的命\N{\b0\fs12}She can't save your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有人可以的\N{\b0\fs12}No one can, not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.06,0:22:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我只求一個痛快\N{\b0\fs12}All I ask is for is a quick death.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.56,0:22:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你不配那麼快解脫\N{\b0\fs12}You don't deserve a quick death.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.69,0:22:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\b0\fs12}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.26,0:22:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但我依然請求你們\N{\b0\fs12}And I'm still asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.39,0:22:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你的決定\N{\b0\fs12}It's your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.52,0:22:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,快從實說來  艾沃\N{\b0\fs12}Start talking, Ivo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.69,0:22:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我從來沒有成功地\N{\b0\fs12}I was never able to replicate the Mirakuru serum
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,從我發現的二戰時期日本的研究中\N{\b0\fs12}from the original Japanese World War II
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.04,0:22:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,復制出米拉庫魯血清\N{\b0\fs12}research I discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,經過一年的\N{\b0\fs12}After conducting experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.11,0:22:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,人體試驗之後\N{\b0\fs12}on the prisoners that I acquired this past year,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.94,0:22:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我成功合成了一種溶液\N{\b0\fs12}I was able to synthesize a solution
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.60,0:23:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,能夠抵消和逆轉\N{\b0\fs12}that counteracts, reverses
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.24,0:23:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,米拉庫魯所產生的生理效應\N{\b0\fs12}the physiological effects that exposure to Mirakuru produces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,從擁有超人的能力\N{\b0\fs12}From more than human...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,轉變回普通人類\N{\b0\fs12}back to human.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.08,0:23:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,解藥現在在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Where is this cure now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.78,0:23:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你會信守諾言結束我的生命嗎\N{\b0\fs12}You'll keep your word about ending my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,對  快告訴我們\N{\b0\fs12}Yes. Tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.17,0:23:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在貨船上\N{\b0\fs12}On the freighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.31,0:23:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在我房間的保險櫃裡\N{\b0\fs12}In the safe in my quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我想\N{\b0\fs12}Now I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我的這部分已經做完了\N{\b0\fs12}this concludes my end of our deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.46,0:24:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你要說什麼  反正一分鐘內\N{\b0\fs12}Whatever you came here to say, it takes security
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.12,0:24:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,保安就會上來\N{\b0\fs12}about 60 seconds to reach this floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我就陪你聊一會\N{\b0\fs12}so I would start talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.03,0:24:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德在哪裡\N{\b0\fs12}Where's Slade?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.94,0:24:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是給你機會做正確的事\N{\b0\fs12}I just wanted to give you the chance to do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.24,0:24:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不到30歲\N{\b0\fs12}I'm under 30,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.29,0:24:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,擔任著財富500強企業的總裁\N{\b0\fs12}and I'm the CEO of a Fortune 500 company.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.86,0:24:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想這足以說明我做了正確的事\N{\b0\fs12}I'd say I've already done the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.17,0:24:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道斯萊德•威爾遜是什麼樣的人嗎\N{\b0\fs12}And do you even know who Slade Wilson is?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.33,0:24:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,或者他做這些是為了什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Or why he's doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.69,0:24:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎\N{\b0\fs12}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.81,0:24:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-這些都是我應得的  -你應得的\N{\b0\fs12}- I got what I earned. - What you earned?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.73,0:24:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你以為上了我爸爸的床\N{\b0\fs12}You think that sleeping with my father
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.18,0:24:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他的公司就應該屬於你了嗎\N{\b0\fs12}entitles you to my family's company?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.05,0:24:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不知道是怎麼回事\N{\b0\fs12}You have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.70,0:24:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他玩過不少女人\N{\b0\fs12}Wow, he fooled around with a lot of girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.03,0:24:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人可沒有來惡意收購的\N{\b0\fs12}I don't see any of them ordering hostile takeovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.51,0:24:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,玩女人\N{\b0\fs12}Fooled around?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.24,0:24:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你媽是這麼跟你說的嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is that what your mother told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.92,0:24:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她當然會把我說成一個無關緊要的小三\N{\b0\fs12}Of course she would write me off as a meaningless affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.50,0:24:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,斯萊德•威爾遜讓我吃了很大的苦\N{\b0\fs12}Slade Wilson put me through hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.75,0:24:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他的魔鬼訓練差點害死了我\N{\b0\fs12}His training nearly killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.13,0:24:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我只是個被拋棄的情人\N{\b0\fs12}Would I put myself through
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.96,0:24:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我何必要去承受這些\N{\b0\fs12}all that just because I was a jilted lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.74,0:24:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,說實話  我不知道你算什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Honestly, I don't know what you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.98,0:24:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你父親的摯愛\N{\b0\fs12}I was your father's soul mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.84,0:24:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他當時已經準備離開你母親\N{\b0\fs12}He was going to leave your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.09,0:24:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,離開公司  丟下你\N{\b0\fs12}leave the company, leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.30,0:25:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-我們行李都整理好了  -是嗎\N{\b0\fs12}- Our bags were packed. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.27,0:25:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可你妹妹偏偏要摔壞胳膊\N{\b0\fs12}Your sister had to go and break her arm
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.54,0:25:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,做出些蠢事來\N{\b0\fs12}doing something ridiculous, no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.11,0:25:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她從馬背上摔下來了\N{\b0\fs12}She fell off her horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.37,0:25:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他接到電話的時候我們已經到機場了\N{\b0\fs12}We were at the airport when he got the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.66,0:25:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我求他不要回去\N{\b0\fs12}I begged him not to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.86,0:25:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我提醒他西婭甚至不是他親生的\N{\b0\fs12}I reminded him that Thea wasn't even his.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.94,0:25:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你是說我爸爸早就知道\N{\b0\fs12}Are you saying that my father knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.36,0:25:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他當然知道了\N{\b0\fs12}Of course he knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.88,0:25:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他是傻  但不是白癡\N{\b0\fs12}He was a fool, not an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.91,0:25:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就像傻瓜一樣  他還是很疼愛她\N{\b0\fs12}And like a fool, he loved her anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.37,0:25:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他答應我第二天就離開\N{\b0\fs12}He promised me that we would leave the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.87,0:25:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可恰恰相反  我的實習被終止了\N{\b0\fs12}But instead, my internship was terminated
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.11,0:25:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他也再沒跟我說過一句話\N{\b0\fs12}and he never spoke to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.14,0:25:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是為了這個吧\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, so that's what this is really about.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.05,0:25:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他為了我們拋棄了你\N{\b0\fs12}He chose us over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.07,0:25:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,請把奎恩先生請出大樓\N{\b0\fs12}Please escort Mr. Queen off the premises.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.66,0:25:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,別碰我\N{\b0\fs12}Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.60,0:25:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要讓他再進這座大樓了\N{\b0\fs12}He's no longer welcome in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.47,0:25:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的地方\N{\b0\fs12}My building.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.36,0:25:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\b0\fs12}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.72,0:25:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭  我是奧利\N{\b0\fs12}Thea, it's Ollie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.02,0:26:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和你見面談  就五分鐘\N{\b0\fs12}Listen, I just need five minutes face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.06,0:26:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你想幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.31,0:26:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有件事情需要告訴你\N{\b0\fs12}There's something you need to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.44,0:26:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就五分鐘  酒吧關門後來吧\N{\b0\fs12}Five minutes. Come by the club after we close.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.36,0:26:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,剛跟費利西蒂通過話\N{\b0\fs12}Just spoke with Felicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.69,0:26:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有人要找綠箭俠\N{\b0\fs12}Someone reached out to the Arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.65,0:26:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,見面談談\N{\b0\fs12}Wants a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.02,0:26:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰\N{\b0\fs12}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.00,0:26:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.55,0:26:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,待地舒服嗎  蘭斯警官\N{\b0\fs12}You comfortable in there, Officer Lance?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.44,0:26:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你冷的話我可以給你再找條毯子\N{\b0\fs12}I can see if there's an extra blanket if you're cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.55,0:26:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好  既然我現在關在這裡了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm good. But hey, now that I'm on this side of the bars,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.36,0:26:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫我昆汀就行了\N{\b0\fs12}I think it's just Quentin.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.84,0:26:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信這只是個誤會\N{\b0\fs12}I'm sure it's just a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.53,0:26:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你很快就能出去了\N{\b0\fs12}You'll be out of here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.88,0:26:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你的樂觀\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, I appreciate your optimism.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.48,0:26:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.97,0:26:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,夥計\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.72,0:26:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,警官  快來人啊  快來人啊\N{\b0\fs12}Officer! We need help! We need help!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.42,0:26:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你要幹什麼  夥計\N{\b0\fs12}Whoa, whoa, what are you doing, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.52,0:26:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,記得我嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.88,0:27:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你該記得的  因為我記得你  警官\N{\b0\fs12}You should, 'cause I remember you, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.28,0:27:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你不能這麼做\N{\b0\fs12}No, you can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.38,0:27:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的  別緊張\N{\b0\fs12}All right, take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.12,0:27:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因為你和那個穿帽衫的怪胎\N{\b0\fs12}'Cause you and that hooded freak show
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.31,0:27:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我才進了這鬼地方\N{\b0\fs12}are the reason I'm in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.96,0:27:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得我應該過來招呼你一下\N{\b0\fs12}I thought I should be the one to welcome you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.00,0:27:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這還沒完\N{\b0\fs12}This isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.41,0:27:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這沒完\N{\b0\fs12}This is not over!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.73,0:27:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽說你父親被捕了\N{\b0\fs12}I heard about your father being arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.38,0:27:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我可以的話我會幫他的\N{\b0\fs12}If I could help him, I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.07,0:27:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是為了這件事叫你來的\N{\b0\fs12}That's not what this is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.56,0:27:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,很有趣不是嗎\N{\b0\fs12}It's funny, isn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.80,0:27:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一年以前他以為你是個謀殺犯\N{\b0\fs12}A year ago, he thought you were a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.21,0:27:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,而我  我卻被你吸引\N{\b0\fs12}And me, I was-- I was drawn to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.13,0:27:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道這是為什麼  但\N{\b0\fs12}I couldn't explain why, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.60,0:27:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我總覺得我們心靈相通\N{\b0\fs12}but a part of me felt connected to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.90,0:28:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你總是會及時地出現\N{\b0\fs12}You were always there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.24,0:28:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,為了我\N{\b0\fs12}For me...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.80,0:28:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,為了我的家人\N{\b0\fs12}for my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.60,0:28:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,而因為某種原因我從來沒問過為什麼\N{\b0\fs12}and for some reason, I never asked why.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.32,0:28:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你現在是在問我嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Are you asking now?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.61,0:28:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要了\N{\b0\fs12}I don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.82,0:28:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我已經知道答案了\N{\b0\fs12}Because I already know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.27,0:28:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\b0\fs12}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.34,0:28:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸出事了\N{\b0\fs12}It's dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.47,0:28:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼了\N{\b0\fs12}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.50,0:28:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,勞蕾爾  我真的很抱歉\N{\b0\fs12}Laurel, I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.54,0:28:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你父親現在處於保護性監禁\N{\b0\fs12}We had your father under protective custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.49,0:28:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在鐵山監獄根本就沒有保護性監禁可言\N{\b0\fs12}There's no such as thing as protective custody in Iron Heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.83,0:28:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\b0\fs12}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.08,0:28:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事的  寶貝  我沒事\N{\b0\fs12}It's all right, sweetheart, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.81,0:28:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,別 別 別碰我的肋骨\N{\b0\fs12}Hey, whoa, don't touch the ribs! The ribs.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.79,0:29:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我快要厭倦來醫院看我的家人了\N{\b0\fs12}I'm getting tired of visiting my family members in a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.95,0:29:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼了\N{\b0\fs12}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.25,0:29:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,只不過是一個老相識過來拜訪我一下\N{\b0\fs12}Oh, it's just some old collar paid me a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.20,0:29:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我在監獄裡不太受歡迎\N{\b0\fs12}I guess I'm not the most popular guy in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.52,0:29:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉  你介意我和爸爸單獨聊聊嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Sara, do you mind giving Dad and I a second alone, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.92,0:29:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,當然不\N{\b0\fs12}Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.35,0:29:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在外面等著\N{\b0\fs12}I'll be right outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.30,0:29:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,別走太遠  寶貝\N{\b0\fs12}Don't go far, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.65,0:29:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\b0\fs12}Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.66,0:29:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  寶貝\N{\b0\fs12}What is it, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.06,0:29:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-我必須要告訴你一件事  -怎麼了\N{\b0\fs12}- I have to tell you something. - What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.45,0:29:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道綠箭俠是誰了\N{\b0\fs12}I know who the Arrow is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.06,0:29:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.02,0:29:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要講出來\N{\b0\fs12}Don't say another word.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.13,0:29:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不要說\N{\b0\fs12}Don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.48,0:29:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\b0\fs12}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.96,0:29:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著  我曾經寧願不當員警\N{\b0\fs12}Listen to me, there was a time when I would have
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.08,0:29:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,也要找出他的真實身份  你知道的\N{\b0\fs12}sold out my badge to find out his name. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.80,0:29:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但是現在我意識到我已經不在乎了\N{\b0\fs12}But then I realize I didn't care who he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.29,0:29:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,事實上  我甚至不想知道他是誰了\N{\b0\fs12}In fact, I didn't even want to know who he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.15,0:29:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.33,0:29:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我明白一旦我知道了他是誰\N{\b0\fs12}'Cause I knew if I knew who he really was,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.22,0:30:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他就成為了一個真實的人\N{\b0\fs12}then he'd become a person, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.57,0:30:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也許他也有家人和朋友\N{\b0\fs12}Maybe he's got a family. Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.92,0:30:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有在乎他的人\N{\b0\fs12}People that care about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.80,0:30:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他也有自己的生活\N{\b0\fs12}Someone with a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.12,0:30:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣他就不是我需要他成為的樣子了\N{\b0\fs12}That he couldn't be what I needed him to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.90,0:30:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這個城市需要他成為的樣子了\N{\b0\fs12}What this city needs him to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.17,0:30:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,綠箭俠這個角色才重要\N{\b0\fs12}It's the Arrow that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.65,0:30:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,帽衫下面的人是誰無所謂\N{\b0\fs12}The man under the hood isn't important.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.47,0:30:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你能想像他的生活是什麼樣的嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Can you imagine what it's like to be him?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.71,0:30:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他日復一日的生活\N{\b0\fs12}What he has to live with day in and day out,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.76,0:30:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,必須是什麼樣子的\N{\b0\fs12}what that's got to be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.07,0:30:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做的就是坐在這裡給他一些時間\N{\b0\fs12}The least I can do is sit here and do a little bit of time for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.46,0:30:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你父親怎麼樣了\N{\b0\fs12}How's your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.12,0:30:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你放棄對他的指控\N{\b0\fs12}He'll be better once you drop all charges
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.73,0:30:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,在釋放文件上簽字那他就更好了\N{\b0\fs12}and sign his release papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.31,0:30:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他面臨的可是一年半的監禁\N{\b0\fs12}He is facing 18 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.08,0:30:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  不過他不會再待在監獄裡了\N{\b0\fs12}Yes. But he is not going to stay here another day
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.78,0:30:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你想讓我辭職\N{\b0\fs12}unless you want me to resign
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.02,0:31:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,然後開始我的刑事辯護律師生涯\N{\b0\fs12}and embark on an exciting new career as a criminal defense attorney
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.91,0:31:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我唯一的志向就是起訴地方檢察官辦公室\N{\b0\fs12}whose sole ambition will be to sue the District Attorney's office
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.80,0:31:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,非法逮捕和怠忽致危罪\N{\b0\fs12}for wrongful arrest and reckless endangerment.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.05,0:31:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你父親簽了保證書之後\N{\b0\fs12}Your father will be released on his own recognizance
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.66,0:31:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一小時之內就會被釋放\N{\b0\fs12}within the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.59,0:31:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,明天開始復職\N{\b0\fs12}And reinstated. Tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.03,0:31:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,給你一個建議\N{\b0\fs12}A word of advice--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.20,0:31:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,以後要小心選擇你的對手\N{\b0\fs12}be mindful of the battles you choose,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.38,0:31:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因為不是所有爭鬥都像今天這麼容易\N{\b0\fs12}because it will not always be this easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.53,0:31:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,法律顧問幹得漂亮\N{\b0\fs12}Nice work, counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.11,0:31:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.27,0:31:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你的胳膊怎麼樣了\N{\b0\fs12}How's your arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.32,0:31:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,還可以  只有揮手的時候才疼\N{\b0\fs12}Fine. Only hurts when I wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.71,0:31:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事的  向你保證\N{\b0\fs12}I'm fine, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.01,0:31:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你會沒事的\N{\b0\fs12}I know you will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.19,0:31:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.42,0:32:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}威登酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.79,0:32:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你能同意來和我談談\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you for agreeing to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.89,0:32:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是負責來聽你說的\N{\b0\fs12}You're talking. I only agreed to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.83,0:32:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想說\N{\b0\fs12}I just want to start with--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.04,0:32:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你認為\N{\b0\fs12}I know you think that--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.19,0:32:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\b0\fs12}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.67,0:32:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,費利西蒂  我現在沒時間接電話\N{\b0\fs12}I can't talk right now, Felicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.41,0:32:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白  但是柯林斯梅因電網數據突增\N{\b0\fs12}I know. But the grid at Collins and Main just spiked,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.86,0:32:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,顯示為用電量巨大\N{\b0\fs12}drawing a hell of a lot of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.19,0:32:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這意味著要麼有人正在使用\N{\b0\fs12}which means someone either
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.22,0:32:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這個世界上最大的吹風機\N{\b0\fs12}plugged in the world's largest hair dryer,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.82,0:32:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要不就是生物疏導器已經開始運行\N{\b0\fs12}or the biotransfuser just went online.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.92,0:32:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這臺機器有特定的動力循環週期\N{\b0\fs12}The power cycle on this machine is very specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.88,0:32:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你有三十分鐘時間  最多四十分鐘\N{\b0\fs12}You have 30 minutes, 40 tops.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.13,0:32:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道這很自私  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}I know this is selfish, Oliver,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.52,0:32:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不要怪我這麼說\N{\b0\fs12}and don't hate me for saying this,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.73,0:32:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  你別去\N{\b0\fs12}but...don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.31,0:32:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果西婭不在那些檔上簽字\N{\b0\fs12}If you don't get Thea to sign those documents,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.98,0:32:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你們家就會失去所有財產\N{\b0\fs12}your family loses all of its assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.00,0:33:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我不馬上阻止斯萊德\N{\b0\fs12}If I don't stop Slade right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.24,0:33:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,會有更多人失去更多財產\N{\b0\fs12}a lot of people will lose a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.12,0:34:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是你的話我可不會碰\N{\b0\fs12}I wouldn't touch that if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.56,0:34:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在運行中動他會害死他的\N{\b0\fs12}Removing him mid-cycle will surely end his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.40,0:34:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-斯萊德  他只是個孩子  -他來這裡\N{\b0\fs12}- Slade, he's just a kid! - Who's here
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.89,0:34:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為你把他拒之門外了\N{\b0\fs12}only because you pushed him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.78,0:34:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他之前敬仰的一直是你\N{\b0\fs12}You were the one person he looked up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.94,0:34:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可是  你卻傷害了他的心靈\N{\b0\fs12}And for that, you crushed his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.73,0:34:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在布魯德海文的一處避難所找到他的\N{\b0\fs12}We found him at a shelter in Bludhaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.71,0:35:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,太可憐了  連抵抗都沒有抵抗\N{\b0\fs12}Pathetic. Didn't even put up a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.15,0:35:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我會抵抗的\N{\b0\fs12}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.69,0:35:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我怎麼關掉\N{\b0\fs12}Tell me how to shut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.50,0:35:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能感受到我體內洶湧的能量\N{\b0\fs12}If you could feel the power that is surging through me...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.45,0:35:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你就會知道我不怕一隻小小的箭\N{\b0\fs12}You would know that I do not fear an arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.42,0:35:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我遠比你想像的要強大的多\N{\b0\fs12}I am stronger than you can even imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.96,0:35:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上...\N{\b0\fs12}And soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.36,0:35:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就會有人跟我一樣了\N{\b0\fs12}I will not be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.46,0:35:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你傷害不了我  小子\N{\b0\fs12}You can't hurt me, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.87,0:36:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,羅伊  來  堅持住\N{\b0\fs12}Come on, Roy. All right, stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.62,0:36:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他失血過多\N{\b0\fs12}He's lost a lot of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.16,0:36:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道生物輸液對他造成了什麼影響\N{\b0\fs12}I don't know what the biotransfuser did to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.11,0:36:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他的脈搏很虛弱  幾乎沒有呼吸了\N{\b0\fs12}But his pulse is really weak; He's barely breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.50,0:36:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他需要真正的醫生\N{\b0\fs12}And he needs a real doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.96,0:36:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不能帶他去醫院  醫院會做各種檢查\N{\b0\fs12}We can't take him to a hospital-- they run tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.54,0:36:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不能讓別人知道他體內有什麼東西\N{\b0\fs12}We need to keep what's in him from getting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.99,0:37:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們該怎麼辦\N{\b0\fs12}What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.09,0:37:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就只能等著\N{\b0\fs12}The only thing we can do-- we wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.69,0:37:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,與此同時  斯萊德的問題還沒有解決\N{\b0\fs12}Well, while we're waiting, we still have a Slade problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.72,0:37:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他還有20個跟他一樣的人\N{\b0\fs12}He's got 20 guys just like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.22,0:37:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我們沒辦法阻止他\N{\b0\fs12}and we have no way to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.12,0:37:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我們有辦法\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.94,0:37:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我想的東西嗎\N{\b0\fs12}Is that what I think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.86,0:37:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,米拉庫魯\N{\b0\fs12}Mirakuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.17,0:37:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你不會是想服下這個吧\N{\b0\fs12}You weren't thinking about taking it, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.31,0:37:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\b0\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.85,0:37:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要用它製造解藥\N{\b0\fs12}We're going to use it to make a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.16,0:37:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗  我們都不知道\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver, we don't even know
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.92,0:37:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,它的作用是不是可逆的\N{\b0\fs12}if it's possible to reverse the affects.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.48,0:37:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我們知道\N{\b0\fs12}Yes, we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.82,0:37:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,艾沃成功過\N{\b0\fs12}Ivo did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.20,0:37:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼不早說  奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Why didn't you ever tell us that, Oliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.31,0:37:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我感覺很慚愧\N{\b0\fs12}Because I'm ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.23,0:37:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼\N{\b0\fs12}Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.38,0:37:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,五年前  我有機會給斯萊德用解藥的\N{\b0\fs12}Five years ago, I had the chance to use the cure on Slade.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.84,0:37:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可我卻選擇了殺他\N{\b0\fs12}I chose to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.53,0:37:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的一切都是我的錯\N{\b0\fs12}Everything that's happening right now is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.42,0:37:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我救過你一次  莎拉\N{\b0\fs12}I saved you once, Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.89,0:37:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺像很久以前的事了\N{\b0\fs12}It feels like a long time ago now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.84,0:38:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你是時候回報我了\N{\b0\fs12}Time to return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.10,0:38:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可能你們不會相信\N{\b0\fs12}You might not believe it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.73,0:38:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但我以前是個好人\N{\b0\fs12}but I was considered a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.72,0:38:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是個好醫生  好丈夫\N{\b0\fs12}A good doctor. A good husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.59,0:38:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可後來米拉庫魯把我變瘋了\N{\b0\fs12}Until the Mirakuru drove me mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.52,0:38:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至沒有讓自己...\N{\b0\fs12}I didn't even take any myself--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.11,0:38:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒必要為我這麼做的\N{\b0\fs12}You didn't have to do that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.93,0:38:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦你殺了人\N{\b0\fs12}Once you take a life...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.57,0:38:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,它會永遠改變你的\N{\b0\fs12}it changes you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.52,0:38:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想讓你那樣\N{\b0\fs12}And I don't want that for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.98,0:38:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\b0\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.26,0:38:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,幸運兒\N{\b0\fs12}Schastlivchik.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.90,0:39:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我們現在怎麼辦\N{\b0\fs12}So, now what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.93,0:39:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你們應該不會有人知道怎麼開潛艇吧\N{\b0\fs12}Well, I don't suppose any of you know how to pilot a submarine?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.04,0:39:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭\N{\b0\fs12}Thea.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.88,0:39:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼呢\N{\b0\fs12}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.93,0:39:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,收拾東西而已  我覺得\N{\b0\fs12}Just grabbing some stuff. Something tells me
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.99,0:39:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡的新主人不想讓我的衣服出現在這裡\N{\b0\fs12}the mansion's new owner won't want my clothes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.82,0:39:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭  等等\N{\b0\fs12}Thea, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.00,0:39:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你不忙了啊\N{\b0\fs12}Now he's not busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.56,0:39:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起  我也無能為力\N{\b0\fs12}I'm so sorry, that couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.03,0:39:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我能跟你說幾句話嗎\N{\b0\fs12}May I speak to you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.80,0:39:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸知道真相\N{\b0\fs12}Dad knew the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.27,0:39:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.59,0:39:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道梅林的事\N{\b0\fs12}He knew about Merlyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.34,0:39:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能\N{\b0\fs12}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.70,0:39:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他從沒跟我提過\N{\b0\fs12}He never said anything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.37,0:39:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,沒這個必要\N{\b0\fs12}He didn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.03,0:39:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,西婭  不論爸爸有什麼錯\N{\b0\fs12}Thea, whatever dad's faults were...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.65,0:39:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他都是愛我們的\N{\b0\fs12}He loved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.30,0:39:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,愛我們所有人\N{\b0\fs12}All of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.92,0:39:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我們是他的家人\N{\b0\fs12}Because we were his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.64,0:39:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你是他女兒\N{\b0\fs12}You were his daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.00,0:39:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,一次破驗血不會改變這點\N{\b0\fs12}and some stupid blood test wasn't going to change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.41,0:40:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他選擇了我們\N{\b0\fs12}He chose us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.19,0:40:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他選擇了你\N{\b0\fs12}He chose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.01,0:40:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他決定\N{\b0\fs12}He made a decision
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.19,0:40:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,做你的父親\N{\b0\fs12}to be your father,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.83,0:40:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,即使他並不是非這樣不可\N{\b0\fs12}even though he didn't have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.15,0:40:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你有什麼感想呢\N{\b0\fs12}So what does that tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.24,0:40:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,感想就是他是個騙子\N{\b0\fs12}It tells me that he's a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.45,0:40:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就跟你們倆一樣\N{\b0\fs12}Just like both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.76,0:40:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}星城實驗室
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.30,0:40:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你們幫我個忙\N{\b0\fs12}I need you guys to do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.72,0:40:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,記得保密\N{\b0\fs12}This time, it'll be our secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.23,0:40:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}威登酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.07,0:40:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,奧利弗\N{\b0\fs12}Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.06,0:41:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這是幹什麼\N{\b0\fs12}What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.19,0:41:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你對我而言很重要\N{\b0\fs12}Because you're important to me.
